data.description: Welcome to "The South Bronx''. This Vyse Avenue 2 family detached home is in move-in condition. The property has 2 units-3 bedrooms,   1 bathroom, living room, kitchen, over 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, living room, and kitchen. There's an unfinished basement, separate boiler and hot water tank. The house is fully rented, with paying tenants.  It is walking distance from #5 & 2 Train, Buses #42 ,19, 36, and the shopping center. It has very low property taxes. A nice backyard. Motivated owner. Please call for additional information.
